</taxonomicName>
by the narrow clypeal region and the light coloured opisthosoma but differs distinctly, also from all other 
<taxonomicName box="[998,1106,1209,1234]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Cerbalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
